{"tid":2153784,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《別告訴她》(The Farewell)導演Lulu Wang翻拍是枝裕和作品《誰調換了我的父親》","createTime":"2020-08-12T18:03:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T03:23:32.000Z","uid":4260,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"430a6202939dcf220e2dd9b2e09c2f9c35658bf3","tid":2153784,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T18:03:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Lulu Wang to Direct English-Language Remake of Kore-eda&rsquo;s &lsquo;Like Father, Like Son&rsquo;</strong><br />\n<br />\nThe long-gestating remake would add to &quot;The Farewell&quot; filmmaker's already packed upcoming slate.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;The Farewell&rdquo; filmmaker Lulu Wang has reportedly added another major product to her growing slate. <span class=\"gold\">Observer reports that Wang has been tapped to direct an English-language remake of the beloved Hirokazu Kore-eda film &ldquo;Like Father, Like Son&rdquo; for Focus Features</span>. A source close to Focus confirms the news, and that it is currently in development at the studio. Playwright Sarah Ruhl has reportedly been attached to write the screenplay and Wang will produce alongside Josh McLaughlin under his Wink Productions banner.<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.indiewire.com/2020/08/lulu-wang-english-language-remake-like-father-like-son-1234579495/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiewire.com%2F2020%2F08%2Flulu-wang-english-language-remake-like-father-like-son-1234579495%2F&d=bHO956KQIgsLkYPN5Vvl7cyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=2f103d35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.indiewire.com/2020/08/lulu-wang-english-language-remake-like-father-like-son-1234579495/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a468ba3fc2be117c5560-f9a6225d634730495a59b91d1543c5a4.ssl.cf5.rackcdn.com/FARETHD-01_KeyArt_Digital_RGB-FIN2_R23.jpg\" data-thumbnail